      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of October 28 Religion Journal column on efforts by some Texas Baptists to end contributions to Southern Baptist Convention</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Religion Journal column on Saturday, about efforts by some Texas Baptists to end contributions to the Southern Baptist Convention because of its conservative policies, misstated the name of the denomination's Texas organization. It is the Baptist General Convention of Texas, not the General Baptist Convention.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>The Religion Journal column on Saturday, about efforts by some Texas Baptists to end contributions to the Southern Baptist Convention because of its conservative policies, misstated the name of the denomination's Texas organization. It is the Baptist General Convention of Texas, not the General Baptist Convention.</p>
      </block>
    </body.content>
